Dorothy Evans (1893 - 22 Septemba 1943) bụ onye isi otu ọrụ na Britain.

A mụrụ ya na Stockport, Evans gụrụ akwụkwọ na Stockport High School, mgbe ahụ ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ Na Mahadum Manchester.  Site na 1918 ruo 1931, ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka odeakwụkwọ ukwu nke Association of Women Clerks and Secretaries (AWCS), ma site na nke a ọ na-arụsi ọrụ ike na Trades Union Congress, na-eje ozi na Standing Joint Committee of Working Women's Organisations.
N'oge ezumike ya, Evans gụrụ akwụkwọ ka ọ bụrụ onye ọka iwu, a kpọkwara ya n'ụlọikpe n'afọ 1925
N'agbanyeghị nke a, ọ nọgidere bụrụ onye ọrụ otu ọrụ
Ọ na-arụkwa ọrụ na Labour Party, o guzoro n'enweghị ihe ịga nke ọma na ntuli aka Paddington South nke 1930.
N'afọ 1931, Evans hapụrụ AWCS wee bụrụ odeakwụkwọ nke National Association of Women Civil Servants
Ọ nwụrụ na 1943, mgbe ọ rịasịrị ọrịa ogologo oge.
